
Regular exercise aids digestion and improves sleep.

My grandfather needs a hearing aid to hear clearly.

He applied for financial aid to help pay for his college tuition.


（規律運動有助於消化並改善睡眠。）
（我爺爺需要戴助聽器才能聽得清楚。）
（他申請了助學金來幫忙支付大學學費。）

